== 经历 ==
'''克里斯·沃森'''指他[[父親|父親]]是[[英國海軍|英國海軍]][[軍人|軍人]]喬治·沃森（George Watson），但[[文獻|文獻]]顯示其父名叫Johan Cristian Tanck，是[[德國人|德國裔]][[智利人|智利人]]；克里斯·沃森生於[[智利|智利]][[瓦爾帕萊索省|瓦爾帕萊索省]][[瓦爾帕萊索|瓦爾帕萊索]]<ref name=adb>{{Australian Dictionary of Biography |last= Nairn |first= Bede |authorlink=  |year= 1990 |id= A120450b |title= Watson, John Christian (1867 - 1941)   |accessdate= 2008-05-19}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://primeministers.naa.gov.au/fastfacts.asp?pmSelectName=4 |title=澳洲總理概覽：沃森 |accessdate=2008-06-20 |archive-date=2008-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080720135754/http://primeministers.naa.gov.au/fastfacts.asp?pmSelectName=4 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.atua.org.au/biogs/ALE1165b.htm |title=澳洲貿易聯盟文檔／傳記：克里斯·沃森 |accessdate=2008-06-20 |archive-date=2020-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200331101908/http://www.atua.org.au/biogs/ALE1165b.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://nla.gov.au/nla.ms-ms451 |title=Guide to the Papers of John Christian Watson - MS 451 |accessdate=2008-06-20 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215813/http://nla.gov.au/nla.ms-ms451 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nma.gov.au/education/school_resources/websites_and_interactives/primeministers/john_watson/ |title=澳洲國家博物館：克里斯·沃森 |accessdate=2008-06-20 |archive-date=2011-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111113023248/http://www.nma.gov.au/education/school_resources/websites_and_interactives/primeministers/john_watson/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。文獻亦顯示克里斯·沃森的[[母親|母親]]馬莎·明欽（Martha Minchin）是紐西蘭人。

